&lt;a rel=&quot;noopener nofollow noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theowenyoung&#x2F;gatsby-theme-timeline&quot;&gt;Timeline&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;, a
